Version 1.0 (2014-01-17)
*  initial rewrite of the web dashboard with these features:
  * simple MVC framework, no routing yet to preserve old urls using GET parameters
  * home page listing all locales
  * locale page summarizing langchecker data
  * active www.mozilla.org bugs for a locale fetched from Bugzilla
  * per locale rss feed with status of lang files + opened bugs
  * json feed of count of opened bugs for all locales for the product dashboard
  * Templates using sandstone design + tabzilla
